			  <h2>Processing Capabilities</h2>
			  <div class='text-left'>
				<hr class='blu'/>
				<p style='margin-top:.5em;'>We specialize in processing steel blanks, leveled sheets, and slit coils.</p>
				<p id='scale'>Our on-site equipment can hold width and length tolerances down to +/-.010 on sheets and blanks.</p>
				<p>Our coil slitter can handle 72 inch wide coils up to 50,000 lbs and hold width tolerances of +/-.005.</p>
			  </div>
